# Session 03 — Image-based curved-surface estimation

Date: 2026-04-17

## Goal

Image-only analogue of N22 (session 03 v3).  The previous iteration of
this session fit a **plane** through per-tile intensity-jump anchors —
too flat to follow real cortical curvature (e.g. the x ≈ 2000 µm dip
on 790322).  This version fits a **quadratic** surface using the same
math as N22: per-column top-of-signal in an anchor band, plus
**quantile-regression IRLS at q = 0.70**.  L2 estimation is dropped
— the CZ L2 signal was ambiguous in the side views.

